{"id":242265,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-北京维权人士曹顺利到国务院新闻办查询/","date":"2012-07-24T13:46:35Z","modified":"2012-07-24T13:46:35Z","title":"维权网 | 北京维权人士曹顺利到国务院新闻办查询遭推诿（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><span> </span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方斌报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分</span><span>左右，北京维权人士曹顺利等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>名维权人士，前往国务院新闻办查询邮寄的关于《国家人权行动计划》的《信息公开申请书》情况，遭到国务院新闻办秘书局的推诿。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据曹顺利介绍，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>因为我在前往国务院新闻办准备递交《信息公开申请书》时，遭到警方扣押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>小时，当天其他维权人士前往国务院新闻办时也被警方拦截，最后大家只能以特快专递的方式邮寄。通过向邮局查询证实，国务院新闻办办公室已于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日上午</span><span>收到此邮件。根据相关规定，国务院新闻办有关部门应该在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>个工作日之内答复，但至今未收到任何回复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>曹顺利在国务院新闻办询问时，值班室称已将信件转交到秘书局，而秘书局称没查到相关的信件。曹顺利追问是没查到还是没处理，何时才有答复，秘书局相关人员对此不予回答。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>另外两位维权人士再次亲自向国务院新闻办递交带数十人维权人士签名的关于《国家人权行动计划》的《信息公开申请书》，工作人员不接待，亦不收材料。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>分左右，有两名警察突然而至，在国务院新闻办盘问两名维权人士。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>，曹顺利等人将《国家人权行动计划》的《信息公开申请书》公开，向社会各界征集意见、建议和签名，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>，曹顺利在前往国务院新闻办准备递交申请书时被警方扣押，随后</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>余名各地维权人士及访民坚持前往国务院新闻办递交申请书，没到达国务院新闻办即遭到警方的拦截，部分人士被抓走关进久敬庄黑监狱中。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>申请信息公开中要求：由来自不同阶层，不同利益的组织和代表组成联席会议，并按照《手册》要求和国际惯例，履行联席会议职能，将起草，制订，实施，监督，评估的过程向社会开放，听取民意，接受监督。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>相关报道请见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/07/blog-post_7438.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/07/blog-post_7438.html</a></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-nGk6LL5DAgQ/UA59z-aJJgI/AAAAAAAAJpg/5WJPmR2pqGs/s1600/%E6%9C%AA%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-nGk6LL5DAgQ/UA59z-aJJgI/AAAAAAAAJpg/5WJPmR2pqGs/s320/%E6%9C%AA%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98.jpg\" width=\"253\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ADSFgxOGPrY/UA593n5d0RI/AAAAAAAAJpo/ajIjIXdeNwE/s1600/%E6%9C%AA%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%981.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"184\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ADSFgxOGPrY/UA593n5d0RI/AAAAAAAAJpo/ajIjIXdeNwE/s320/%E6%9C%AA%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%981.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<p></div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-6450174183692617426?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/655a678287E9A298.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,17850,20534],"tags":[16910,28519]}